{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ７","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚很快的就到了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳要回家了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天在慢慢的黑下来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切怕见阳光的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在准备活动起来做好汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可一动也不动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只紧紧的抱着头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦苦的在那里想着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比想什么算术题目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要想得更难受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是那么孤零零，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一个老外婆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了打瞌睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是卜读卜读的念她的经。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向外婆要主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外婆一点也听不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次都是这么说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不要吵我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求求菩萨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨保佑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨保佑！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，今晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖就要来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨菩萨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屁用也没有。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿听外婆的话求菩萨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但自己另外又想不出好办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己年纪小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又没有枪或刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是急得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘤嘤嘤的哭起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗡嗡嗡，嗡嗡嗡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里来个小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭得这么凶？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是你呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么哭？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么叫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是不是想吃糖？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我送点蜜你尝一尝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它比糖更甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它比糖更香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羞啊，羞啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个能干有用的小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭哭啼啼象个什么样？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“蜂奶奶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不要冤枉我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是你是我呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怕早已急得躲进了你那小窝窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是想吃糖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是瞎吵闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伤心的哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁也不肯来帮助我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要来把我吃掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要做他的晚餐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在伤心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在不愿！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个老流氓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想把你吃掉吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有好办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定帮助你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好的躲起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果老山妖来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用针刺他的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要他看不见路也摸不着门！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“蜂奶奶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我谢谢你的好意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一向就住在老山妖的花园里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采花酿蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳舞唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样肯来帮助我？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世故不深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种整天只知道又吃又睡的糊涂虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我辛辛苦苦采来花汁酿好蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他轻轻易易的吃得干干净。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我替他卖了力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还嫌我们太吵闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不能好好睡午觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我的小孩子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶得满天飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满地跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对我们一向又和气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定要帮助你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定要帮助你。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正说着说着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖可已经走到山坡上了。（未完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}